Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.50,0:00:38.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10\fad(1000,0)}\N\N\N\N\N\N「祈祷的思慕」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.15,0:00:10.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.94,0:00:14.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别责备他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.28,0:00:17.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总比勉强去战斗送死来的好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.64,0:00:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无谓牺牲  一点意义都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.71,0:00:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在有意义的死法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.00,0:00:29.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:32.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带我去…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.15,0:00:35.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…黄泉那里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.62,0:01:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追踪部队二班  沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:12.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与三班的联络也断绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.41,0:01:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通信机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.29,0:01:19.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是地上班
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.95,0:01:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追踪谏山黄泉的部队的联络断绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.64,0:01:26.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们无法帮上忙  抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.96,0:01:28.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法帮上忙？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.63,0:01:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西坐着感觉还是相当不错的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.60,0:01:35.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是没有你们的协助
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.91,0:01:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在都还身陷在高速公路的堵车里而进退两难呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.47,0:01:41.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.34,0:01:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提箱子的家伙在吗  短发的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.99,0:01:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想对向他拔枪的事情道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.76,0:01:54.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.81,0:01:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  请节哀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.83,0:02:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.63,0:02:06.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵力分布观测班被谏山给歼灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.67,0:02:10.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能根据灵气去追她了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:13.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大致的位置就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.34,0:02:16.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近之后石头便会告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:21.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀生石…在共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意识…要被夺走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.37,0:02:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感情…全涌上来了…无法抑制…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.33,0:02:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念…悲伤…憎恨…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.33,0:02:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我吗…这是真正的我吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:03:02.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…我所期望的感情吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.83,0:03:04.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:11.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和杀生石完全融合的话  你就会完全依照自己的欲望而行动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就会毁掉这个你所憎恨的世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.92,0:03:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀生石…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.16,0:03:39.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的可以实现我的愿望吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.73,0:03:52.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真正的愿望…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.81,0:03:57.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在附近  放我下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:04:00.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降低高度  准备降落
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.03,0:04:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.29,0:04:25.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在  感觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.20,0:04:34.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  集体欢迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.36,0:04:38.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谏山也被杀生石吸引过来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.44,0:04:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来场复仇之战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.06,0:04:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳布  开战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:14.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真强…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.21,0:05:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,类型D
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.91,0:05:40.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐  我们来掩护你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.64,0:05:43.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳布  来保护神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:44.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.02,0:06:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.78,0:06:17.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够慢的呐  神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.60,0:06:20.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过都平安就再好不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:23.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令尊  还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:30.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很久没和爸爸那样谈过了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.27,0:06:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头一次见到那么温柔的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.46,0:06:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头一次感觉到家人的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那也是最后一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.01,0:06:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.86,0:06:48.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真正的家人在小时候就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.03,0:06:52.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收养了我的爸爸就是新的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有你这妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.28,0:06:59.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切就好像是真的家庭一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:02.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:05.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…黄泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:10.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直相信黄泉是没有错的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:14.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只是这样是不行的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:21.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的一厢情愿反而伤害了黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:28.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论事实如何  我都要理解黄泉并支持你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.69,0:07:33.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的信任  应该是这样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.83,0:07:36.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:41.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样  我也要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.62,0:07:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在杀我之前？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是临终遗言？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:51.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果如何马上就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.21,0:07:56.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱红莲！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.22,0:08:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请求你  助我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.85,0:08:08.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喰灵解放
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:10.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白叡！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.42,0:08:37.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次拔刀了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.21,0:08:40.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  你能砍下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:55.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:08:59.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真会开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:09.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱红莲  咆哮波
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.93,0:09:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白叡！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.74,0:09:38.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我听听你是怎么求饶的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:44.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我就让你走得痛快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.11,0:09:47.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥姐她是求过了的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.47,0:09:51.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽叔也是狼狈不堪地挣扎着死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.42,0:09:55.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱庭一骑最后是哭得一塌糊涂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.88,0:09:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神宫寺室长也是  二阶堂桐也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爬在地上  丑陋地哭喊着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:06.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲又怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.15,0:10:08.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死得很惨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很好  你不是想要灵兽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲死掉的话就能得到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我吧  他死的时候  你其实有点高兴的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么瞧不起我  土宫神乐！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:50.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你继承到了白叡和力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.30,0:10:52.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就理解其中的意义吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.01,0:10:53.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.30,0:11:08.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪之
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:10.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.53,0:11:11.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:15.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱红莲  咆哮波
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.63,0:11:22.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐  这边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.35,0:11:41.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  小纪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:50.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…下不了手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.56,0:11:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那已经…不是黄泉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.42,0:11:59.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是被杀生石依附的亡灵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:03.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不杀她  世上一切生物都会被杀尽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:10.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在共同沟见过她了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.36,0:12:15.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说「杀了我」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:21.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说过「杀了我」！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.16,0:12:24.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.77,0:12:25.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.65,0:12:28.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你恨我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.37,0:13:09.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好觉悟了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.91,0:13:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.78,0:13:22.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱除在人世间散布死亡污秽之物正是我们退魔师的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.71,0:13:27.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  过来  神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:31.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来了  黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:41.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面  我叫谏山黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们做姐妹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:50.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  神乐好可爱哟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.24,0:13:52.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:53.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.14,0:13:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:56.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.45,0:13:59.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只有你  神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.13,0:14:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我最后的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.96,0:14:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:11.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢你了  黄泉姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.10,0:14:19.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就识破了  告诉过你两败俱伤与败北无异！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.32,0:14:22.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就结束了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.35,0:14:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀生石…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.61,0:14:39.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你要我顺从欲望而行的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.13,0:14:43.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你明白我真正的愿望是什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:46.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真正的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.10,0:14:48.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的祈求
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.35,0:14:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.72,0:14:55.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要保护那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:59.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想保护她免受一切不幸的摧残
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:03.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想保护她免受一切灾厄的蹂躏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤害她的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:08.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威胁她的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.03,0:15:11.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降祸她的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:14.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想消除这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.78,0:15:18.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你  保护那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.61,0:15:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消除灾厄  抹除祸事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.09,0:15:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:33.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…那就是我自己！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.12,0:16:09.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你变强了  神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.12,0:16:12.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.60,0:16:17.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…变强了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:27.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的…是我骄傲的妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.54,0:16:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.78,0:16:38.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.27,0:17:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在…不要过来…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:17.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我…是不会留情的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:24.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白叡！吃吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.69,0:17:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对杀死了最重要的人的神乐来说  已经没有什么不能下手的了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.39,0:17:54.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘却一切伤痛就可以完成退魔师的职责了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.68,0:17:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  错了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.23,0:18:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘却伤痛  不再受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.57,0:18:04.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这样就不会再有重要的人出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.61,0:18:07.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我们一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.88,0:18:08.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳布
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐还年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:15.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抛弃人心还为时太早
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:22.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要背负这伤痛活下去也还是太年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.72,0:18:28.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…这要看她了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.34,0:18:45.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以一个思念就扭转了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.61,0:18:50.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的意念强大到可以凌驾杀生石之上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说杀生石将她的愿望给…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.87,0:19:01.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罢了  反正事情还没完
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:08.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在时机来临之前  我还有时间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.60,0:19:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}2年后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.27,0:19:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  神宫寺小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.42,0:19:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  小桐人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在中庭  今天天气好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.95,0:19:32.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菖蒲姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.08,0:19:35.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你感觉怎么样  小桐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.75,0:19:37.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了噩梦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:38.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.08,0:19:43.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿黑衣服的女人刺了我的肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.65,0:19:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菖蒲姐也在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.21,0:19:50.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉我们死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.35,0:19:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.73,0:19:55.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后那个黑衣人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.99,0:19:58.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那样走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.95,0:20:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着好像很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:06.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一直都会陪我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:09.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然  一直会陪你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.24,0:20:11.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.38,0:20:15.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  和他分手是对的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥的占卜真灵验啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.05,0:20:24.09,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（灵感占卜  狐使饭纲）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.16,0:20:20.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有点小窍门啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.43,0:20:24.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  也教教咱那窍门啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.25,0:20:27.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行呀  那你也教教我你的事情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:33.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个月里的第二支了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.61,0:20:36.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新任务的命令下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是隐居了吗  不死子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.27,0:20:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许…是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.83,0:20:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两年前她突然消失后回到普通的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.11,0:20:57.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时会想那些幽灵鬼怪是不是真的存在啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.54,0:20:59.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道还会不会再见面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.53,0:21:13.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望她还那么精神就好了  神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.20,0:21:21.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种时候你还真能吃得下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.08,0:21:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好啦  不吃没精神啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.71,0:21:28.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真亏你不觉得这些东西恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.83,0:21:31.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好啦  习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.91,0:21:34.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿剑也早点熟悉那家伙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.38,0:21:39.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空压式·退魔居合刀舞蹴拾贰号
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.85,0:21:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我送你的圣诞礼物哦  阿剑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.33,0:21:48.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是…受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.92,0:21:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东京名胜变成这样可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.30,0:21:57.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快解决完这事吧  神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.77,0:21:58.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.84,0:22:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱除在人世间散布死亡污秽之物正是我们退魔师的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.12,0:22:08.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喰灵解放
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.86,0:22:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白叡！
